rows.name: Me ask that friend buy this, too!
I'm on patrol today!
I see, I see...

Heeey!
Pull me up, will ya?!
Resources aplenty, meh...
Does it look fixable?
...There's not enough stuff here.
Another peaceful day in Torigo...
I wish father would come home soon...

I wanna get my Blade good Core
Chips...
Such nice picture of landscape...
That fish looks delish!
It's a whopper of a catch!
How much for this, please?
So the windmill grinds the flour?
That's right!
Where do kids get the energy...?
I like this playground a lot.
This last order was pretty hefty.
Actually, I like to stay busy.

That's so cold!
I'll get you for that one!
Ahhh! So cold!
I wonder what's past the horizon...

I hear there are some hot places,
and some cold places, too.

Is this spot good for fishing?
Let's find out!

I think you'd have better luck fishing
in Coolley Lake outside Torigo.
Wanna go to the harbor?
I'd love to go ogle some new makeup.
That Edward sure likes fishing, huh?

That place look like good
for salvaging.

It look awfully deep...
Friend go yourself.

Ah!
I saw a fish!

If I bring it home, d'you think
my ma will like it?
Just look at those water wheels!

Using falling water for power?
Clever, very clever...
Toodley-doo～♪

Dam-de-ram～♪
Pam-pam～♪
Great, now it stuck in my head too...
Squee!

Ooh!
So enchanting!

There was some disturbance at the
base lately.
No clue what it's about.

What, what?!
Go away, meh!

There's some brouhaha going on
at that pier over there.
Might go check it out later.
Is this the last of the luggage?
Yeah, this should be all of it.
Are you taking this boat?
That's right.
Watch out!

It's fiiine.
Fine, fine, fine.

Me have news, straight from boat
from Avaritia! Is perfect for any
rumor-loving Gula friends!

I should get my family a souvenir.
But what...?
Hey, pass me that drink, would you?
Roger that.
Thanks for sharing the other day!
Don't mention it.
Let's try sneaking into the base again!

I don't wanna... We got an earful the
last time they found us...
That Gulan kid's always there.
Is she trying to make friends, or what?

There's so many flowers
I've never seen before!

You don't know how to climb trees?
Lemme teach you!
I don't know if I can...
Let's go look at Armus!

The big ones are scary!
And there's a lot of big ones...
What's this building here?

It's the Consulate.
It's where some big-wigs work.
Ah, that's a nice view...
Shall we go shopping later?

Not a bad idea.
So long as there's drinking!
What an enormous windmill.
Yeah, it's a good view from here.

Are you gonna be a soldier
when you grow up?
I'd rather just carry stuff.

That doesn't belong
in this tranquil scene.

I guess so, but...
what're you gonna do?

I think I might get some
meat at the base today.

Ahoy there!
Need a hand?
Ugh, gotta go home and start cooking...
C'mon, let's play together!

After we take this little guy
back to the farm.
One! Two! Three! Four!
Outdated equipment? Again?

Quit your whining.
It's the butt-end of the Empire,
what do you expect?
Is this all the goods for transport?

Some more bits and
bobs are still coming.

It's another cheerful day
here in the woods.

Huh, I wonder.
D'you think Gula's Divine Beast is happy?
'Cos I think so.

Yeah, come to think of it,
all this is part of the Divine Beast...

Me come to buy lumber!
And sell daily use goods in return!
Wood's gotten awfully cheap recently.

If we take quality wood from Gula
and use to reinforce Goldmund...
Oh, be still my beaty-beaty heart!
Ughhh...

...Bleurgh, I knew I shouldn't have
drunk so much last night...
You write home often?

Actually, I haven't lately...
Maybe I ought to.

They're researching ways to make
Archelon even more powerful back
in the fatherland!
Let's hope that pans out.
I'll not lose to a soldier!

Looking good, though I'll remind you
we're meant to be on break...

There's no way I can work
all the way up there...

Huh? How did you keep it together on
the Divine Beast Battleship on the way here?

Stop! Don't hurt!
Me just come to deliver parcel!
Every time same mistake! Why! Why??!!
Time for a breather...

Hey, I want to ride number eight.
Move those plates, would you?

What're you on about?
Asshole.

Uhh...
No, sorry, can't hear a thing.
Not so many casualties lately...

Man, I'm a sucker for that look of
disdain Meleph-sama's got going on.
...Hey, are you all right?
Please grab those vegetables for me.

I'm staring at the sky,
looking at passing birds.

That windmill never ceases
to amaze me.
Um, about our next shipping route...
As a general rule, here's what you do...

We must be able to adapt
to any and all circumstances.

A farm, next-door to the base?
Just wow.
Peace has made these people soft.

Whaddya think of this scenery?
Pretty great, huh?
There's a lot of 'em...
It's food, isn't it?
I don't know what to do now...
Why do we have to leave?!

I'm sorry...
I've got orders to not let you pass.
Please hurry it up.
Brrrrrrrr...
Let us out, meh...

The info broker's got a rumor about a
Divine Beast that's been launched! Curious!
